talkOther.text: Hmm... I wonder who this Cyril guy is, who is mentioned everywhere here.
Some markings in the floor seem to point towards the opposite wall
I see lots of books about bringing back the dead... I have a bad feeling...
I my god! Here it is! Granner was brought back to life by a guy called Cyril!
I see signs of a dark ritual performed here not too long ago...
